[[!meta title="Grass for his pillow"]]
[[!tag books books/fantasy]]

A continuation of the tales of the Otori by Lian Hearn. In this, our
hero strikes off for his own, shrugging off the dictates of the others
in his life, for the first time acting as an individual. While not
nearly as good as it was hyped out to be, it is not a bad tale.

